# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok ireland 's first female cabinet minister said monday she will not run for office again because of press reports about her son 's fistfights at school .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Ireland"))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :mod (c2 / cabinet)
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1)))
            :mod (f / female))
      :ARG1 (r / run-02
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (o2 / office)
            :mod (a / again)
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (r2 / report-01
                        :ARG0 (p2 / press)
                        :ARG1 (f2 / fight-01
                              :ARG0 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                                          :ARG1 p
                                          :ARG2 (s2 / son)))
                              :location (s3 / school)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok researchers have found #,###-year-old human bones in the andes mountains of western argentina , reports here said sunday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (r / report-01
            :location (h / here))
      :ARG1 (f / find-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (r2 / research-01))
            :ARG1 (b / bone
                  :part-of (h2 / human)
                  :age (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year)))
            :location (m / mountain
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Andes")
                  :part-of (w / world-region
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Western"
                              :op2 "Argentina"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the new alitalia took off tuesday but workers marred its launch with protests in rome and milan that caused some flight cancellations and delays .
# ::alignments
(c / contrast-01
      :ARG1 (t / take-off-19
            :ARG1 (a / aircraft-type
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "ALitalia")
                  :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))
      :ARG2 (m / mar-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (w / work-01))
            :ARG1 (l / launch-01
                  :ARG1 a)
            :manner (p2 / protest-01
                  :location (a2 / and
                        :op1 (c2 / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Rome"))
                        :op2 (c3 / city
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Milan")))
                  :ARG0-of (c4 / cause-01
                        :ARG1 (a3 / and
                              :op1 (c5 / cancel-01
                                    :ARG1 (f / fly-01))
                              :op2 (d2 / delay-01
                                    :ARG1 f)
                              :quant (s / some))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the stock market resumed its climb wednesday as a weaker dollar lifted gold prices and federal reserve officials signaled that borrowing rates would remain low .
# ::alignments
(r / resume-01
      :ARG0 (m / market
            :mod (s / stock))
      :ARG1 (c / climb-01
            :ARG0 m)
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (l / lift-01
                        :ARG0 (d / dollar
                              :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG2 (w2 / weak-02
                                          :ARG1 d)
                                    :ARG3 (m2 / more)))
                        :ARG1 (p / price-01
                              :ARG1 (g / gold)))
                  :op2 (s2 / signal-07
                        :ARG0 (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (r2 / reserve-01
                                          :mod (f / federal))
                                    :ARG2 (o / official)))
                        :ARG1 (r3 / remain-01
                              :ARG1 (r4 / rate
                                    :mod (b / borrow-01))
                              :ARG3 (l2 / low-04
                                    :ARG1 r4))))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :op2 "Reault"))
      :ARG1 (p2 / pass-on-09
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (w / win-01
                  :ARG0 p)
            :time (y / year
                  :mod (f / final)
                  :part-of (f2 / formula
                        :mod 1)))
      :time (t / then
            :op1 (p3 / pass-on-09
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (k / know-how
                        :mod (t2 / technology)
                        :poss p)
                  :time (a / after
                        :op1 (n2 / now)
                        :duration (t3 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 2
                              :unit (y2 / year))))))

                        :ARG1 (v / voice
                              :poss (s2 / station
                                    :ARG0-of (r / relay-01
                                          :ARG1 (r2 / radio))
                                    :mod (c4 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "America")))
                              :location (c5 / city
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Kuwait"))))
                  :ARG1 c)
            :ARG1-of (p2 / public-02)
            :time (t / today)))

                        :mod (p / passenger)
                        :poss c)
                  :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                        :ARG1 l)
                  :ARG3 (m / more)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :month 11))
            :op2 (h3 / have-degree-91
                  :ARG1 l
                  :ARG2 h2
                  :ARG1 l)
            :ARG3 (m2 / more)
            :time (b / before
                  :op1 (n2 / now)
                  :quant (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year))))
      :ARG1-of (h4 / help-01
            :ARG0 (ii / include-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / airline
                        :ARG1-of (a3 / acquire-01
                              :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)))))
      :time (w / wednesday))
